text: Anizy-le-Château is a former commune. It is found in the region Hauts-de- France in the Aisne department in the north of France. On 1 January 2019, it was merged into the new commune of Anizy-le-Grand.Arrêté préfectoral == References == Category:Former communes in Aisne
title: Anizy-le-Château
